OL,6,GBBC News will launch a revised
OL,7,Gschedule this March which will leave
OL,8,Gthe service with no planned facility
OL,9,Gto cover UK breaking news stories.
OL,11,FExisting UK-only programmes on the
OL,12,FBBC News Channel will come to an end
OL,13,Fnext week. From 6th March, a new
OL,14,Fjoint UK/international schedule will
OL,15,Fsee UK viewers receive programmes
OL,16,Fincluding World Business Report.
OL,18,FInternational viewers will see
OL,19,Fregular news programmes including
OL,20,FLive, Impact and Global replaced by
OL,21,Fthe new service.
OL,3,CJoint UK/international BBC News
OL,4,Cservice from March
