OL,6,FDetails of the changes were
OL,7,Fexclusively revealed on Pres Cafe on
OL,8,FThursday evening, the forum operated
OL,9,Fby the TV Pres group, of which this
OL,10,Fwebsite is a member.
OL,12,FThe schedule will be temporary to
OL,13,Fallow staff and resources to be used
OL,14,Fto prepare for the full launch of the
OL,15,Fcombined channel this April. But
OL,16,Fduring this time, the BBC will
OL,17,Ftemporarily lose the ability to go
OL,18,Flive to UK viewers only, in the event
OL,19,Fof a UK-specific breaking news story.
OL,3,CJoint UK/international BBC News
OL,4,Cservice from March
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
