OL,6,FAd breaks on the international
OL,7,Fversion of the new channel will be
OL,8,Ffilled with UK-focussed content for
OL,9,FUK viewers. It's not known if World
OL,10,FNews America will appear on the UK
OL,11,Fversion of the channel later in
OL,12,FMarch, when the time difference
OL,13,Fbetween the UK and USA shrinks by one
OL,14,Fhour due to the USA starting daylight
OL,15,Fsavings (summer time) earlier than in
OL,16,Fthe UK.
