OL,6,FNormally, this time difference
OL,7,Fresults in changes to the evening
OL,8,Fschedule, pushing The Context to
OL,9,Fstart half an hour later in the UK.
OL,10,FElsewhere in the evenings, the
OL,11,Fcurrent 'branded' schedule will
OL,12,Fcontinue on both services, with
OL,13,FOutside Source and The Context
OL,14,Fcontinuing as normal.
OL,16,FFrom April, the BBC plans to use
OL,17,FStudio A, its basement studio with a
OL,18,Fvirtual backdrop, to deliver a back-
OL,19,Fup UK breaking news facility as and
OL,20,Fwhen required. This back-up will be
OL,21,Fin operation between 9am and 11pm (UK
OL,22,Ftime).
