OL,6,FThe latest developments follow
OL,7,Fwarnings by regulator Ofcom that it
OL,8,Fexpects the BBC to continue
OL,9,Fdelivering high quality news content
OL,10,Ffor UK audiences. It's threatened to
OL,11,Fimpose conditions on the BBC if this
OL,12,Fdoesn't happen.
OL,3,CJoint UK/international BBC News
OL,4,Cservice from March
